Enhancement Points

Enhancement Points

Use enhancement points to unlock spaces on allies' enhancement boards and to obtain passives with force effects.

*Enhancement Boards will be added sequentially for each character.
Please refer to the in-game notices to learn more about the release schedule.
Obtaining Enhancement Points

Complete quests with icon to earn enhancement points.


Limit on Enhancement Points Obtained During Events

Enhancement points obtained during events have an upper limit.
Some events share the same upper limit.


Rules on Obtaining Enhancement Points

The following rules apply to enhancement points.

• Enhancement points are shared among all characters.
• You can carry up to 999,999 points.
• You will obtain them based on battle results.
The higher the quest difficulty, the more points you gain.
• Quantity boosts from support items, double EXP, or the like do not apply.
• During limited-time events, enhancement points can generally be obtained for the two weeks after the release of permanent content such as new chapters and Lost Chapters. *For more details, please check the notices for each event.
